{"tid":612032,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】狂賀美久奈子Double Center，芽瑠進選拔 Day189 21/3","createTime":"2018-03-31T14:51:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T18:32:47.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"33620ee43db3f2ab9e3096e77f272a2496db4489","tid":612032,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T14:51:58.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=icx43JrqEyES0dg6tHeT1DOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=338b050b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，<br />\n希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=icx43JrqEyES0dg6tHeT1DOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=88106ffc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a></div>"},{"pid":"46a377510ca5b94be5803396077c1793b9f58f11","tid":612032,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T14:59:20.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06feabc7c3ca0e4bbec55d25cfaf902fdd42a365","tid":612032,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T15:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6d6bec37f91f2e88517fe11fa1f9bed6e54822",